                      Octave-throbber
                            ***
          Simple throbber-functionality for Octave

              Written by Anders Dubgaard, 2011

      This is public domain software, see UNLICENSE or
             http://www.unlicense.org/UNLICENSE


This throbber works well in long loops, where it's nice to
see that somethings is being done, but without filling up
the screen with lines and lines of the current loop counter.
